    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898560/extras/c4294ba2f19b59ceb9f4ac99f6e02268.poster.avif?t=1765356176\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898560/extras/c4294ba2f19b59ceb9f4ac99f6e02268.webm?t=1765356176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898560/extras/c4294ba2f19b59ceb9f4ac99f6e02268.mp4?t=1765356176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Pillars of Light</strong> is a <strong>first person puzzle game</strong> that will let you control the power of <strong>light </strong>against shadows.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Carry on your legacy</h2>You will help <strong>Utu</strong>, the light god, to protect the world after your father's death.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight against shadows</h2>To solve the puzzles, you will have to mix light colors, move crates around, ask for Utu to help you, jump and sprint to avoid monsters around. You will have to explore dark places and move carefully in area the shadows control.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898560/extras/121cdc10f50677840ee472f311d32196.poster.avif?t=1765356176\" width=596 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898560/extras/121cdc10f50677840ee472f311d32196.webm?t=1765356176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898560/extras/121cdc10f50677840ee472f311d32196.mp4?t=1765356176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore forgotten worlds</h2>You'll have to visit many places from a lost temple to an old dungeon, each with its own atmosphere, puzzles and dedicated OST<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898560/extras/91a230bb4ceef03482cf9e21b82ebbfd.poster.avif?t=1765356176\" width=604 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898560/extras/91a230bb4ceef03482cf9e21b82ebbfd.webm?t=1765356176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898560/extras/91a230bb4ceef03482cf9e21b82ebbfd.mp4?t=1765356176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
